but%20the%20parents%20had%20already%20left%20for%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20woman%20was%20probably%20killed%20the%20night%20of%20April%2030%20to%20May%201%2C%20according%20to%20surveillance%20camera%20footage%20showing%20five%20people%20leaving%20the%20family%20home%20with%20shovels%2C%20crowbars%20and%20buckets%2C%20before%20returning%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%20Abbas's%20body%20was%20found%20in%20an%20abandoned%20farmhouse%20with%20a%20broken%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20brother%20told%20police%20that%20he%20had%20overheard%20his%20father%20talking%20about%20the%20murder%20and%20that%20it%20was%20the%20uncle%20who%20had%20killed%20his%20sister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%2C%20Shabbar%20Abbas%2C%20was%20arrested%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20extradited%20to%20Italy%20in%20August%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20uncle%2C%20Danish%20Hasnain%2C%20was%20turned%20over%20by%20French%20authorities%20while%20the%20cousins%20were%20arrested%20in%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20men%20were%20present%20at%20the%20trial%2C%20but%20the%20mother%2C%20Nazia%20Shaheen%2C%20is%20still%20a%20fugitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703034120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-12%2Fcourt-generic-650x400_650x400_81450530482.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-couple-in-italy-gets-life-in-jail-for-killing-daughter-for-rejecting-arrange-marriage-4706123%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Pakistani%20couple%20was%20sentenced%20to%20life%20in%20prison%20by%20an%20Italian%20court%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20the%202021%20murder%20of%20their%20daughter%20after%20she%20refused%20an%20arranged%20marriage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonic