tioned%20along%20the%20front%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F12%2F19%2Feurope%2Fukraine-soldiers-russia-frontlines-cmd-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20CNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20their%20experiences%2C%20reporting%20a%20recent%20surge%20in%20the%20use%20of%20tear%20gas%2C%20which%20is%20purportedly%20being%20dropped%20by%20Russian%20drones%20into%20trenches.%20At%20least%20nine%20chemical%20attacks%20have%20bene%20reported%2C%20and%20there%20has%20been%20at%20least%20one%20fatality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20Ukrainian%20service%20members%20affected%20by%20the%20gas%20gave%20a%20horrifyingly%20detailed%20account%20of%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20first%20I%20saw%20smoke%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20ran%20out%20from%20the%20trench%20and%20the%20gas%20suddenly%20caught%20fire.%20The%20trench%20was%20in%20flames.%20This%20gas%20burns%2C%20blinds%20you%2C%20you%20can't%20breathe%2C%20shoots%20down%20your%C2%A0throat%20immediately.%20We%20didn't%20even%20have%20a%20second.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20tear%20gas%20%E2%80%94%20a%20flammable%20chemical%20agent%20which%20can%20cause%20severe%20eye%2C%20respiratory%2C%20and%20skin%20irritation%20and%2C%20in%20particularly%20high%20concentrations%2C%20permanent%20injuries%20and%20death%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20documented%20in%20past%20wars%2C%20but%20its%20use%20in%20warfare%2C%20along%20with%20other%20riot%20control%20agents%2C%20is%20prohibited%20under%20the%20United%20Nations'%20Chemical%20Weapons%20Convention.%20There%20have%20been%20other%20documented%20cases%20of%20Russia%20using%20tear%20gas%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20and%20Russia%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20a%20laundry%20list%20of%20war%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20naval%20forces%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fukrainian_navy%2F1475%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3r0BXWQJR6C1swaNS4TtCNBEnk0ralFVDkhLydzScLnjMkjWKCWM2__1Q%5C%22%20target%