cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmonique-olivier-found-guilty-of-being-involved-in-murders-of-three-women-including-british-student-joanna-parrish-by-ogre-of-the-ardennes-13033662%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmonique-olivier-found-guilty-of-being-involved-in-murders-of-three-women-including-british-student-joanna-parrish-by-ogre-of-the-ardennes-13033662%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haryana%20To%20Recruit%2010%2C000%20Workers%20For%20Israel%2C%20Opposition%20Trains%20Guns%20On%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStruggling%20with%20a%20high%20unemployment%20rate%2C%20the%20Haryana%20government%20has%20released%20an%20advertisement%20recruiting%2010%2C000%20construction%20workers%20who%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20Israel%2C%20a%20country%20that%20has%20been%20locked%20in%20a%20war%20with%20Hamas%20for%20over%20two%20months%20and%20faces%20an%20acute%20shortage%20of%20labourers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advertisement%20has%20been%20criticised%20both%20by%20some%20workers%20and%20the%20opposition%2C%20who%20have%20slammed%20the%20state%20for%20considering%20sending%20Indians%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bwarzone%26quot%3B.%20It%20was%20posted%20just%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20informed%20Parliament%20that%20no%20discussions%20have%20been%20held%20with%20Israel%20regarding%20a%20possible%20replacement%20of%20Palestinian%20construction%20workers%20with%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20government%20has%2C%20however%2C%20defended%20the%20move%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20aim%20was%20to%20ensure%20that%20travel%20agents%20cannot%20fleece%20people%20by%20offering%20them%20jobs%20in%20other%20countries%20and%20that%20there%20is%20no%20compulsion%20for%20labourers%20to%20go%20to%20Israel%20if%20they%20are%20not%20comfortable%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20health%20ministry%20in%20Gaza%2C%20at%20least%2019%2C600%20people%20-%20most%20of%20them%20women%20and%20children%20-%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20attacks%20on%20the%20strip%20of%20land%20since%20October%207%2C%20when%20Hamas%20launched%20a%20multi-pronged%20attack%20on%20the%20Jewish%20country%2C%20killing%20around%201%2C200%20civilians.%20Around%20240%20people%20had%20also%20been%20taken%20hostage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmployment%20Dilemma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advertisement%2C%20which%20appeared%20in%20some%20newspapers%20on%20December%2015%2C%20was%20issued%20by%20the%20Haryana%20Kaushal%20Rojgar%20Nigam%2C%20a%20state%20public%20sector%20company.%20It%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Haryana%20has%20the%20highest%20unemployment%20rate%20in%20the%20country%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%20(CMIE)%2C%20and%20Israel%20is%20facing%20a%20massive%20shortage%20of%20construction%20workers%20because%20of%20the%20cancellation%20of%20work%20permits%20of%20around%2090%2C000%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unemployment%20rate%20in%20Haryana%20was%202.9%20per%20cent%20in%202013-14%20(when%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power)%2C%20which%20increased%20to%209%20per%20cent%20in%202021-22.%20%C2%A0As%20of%20July%2031%2C%202023%2C%205.44%20lakh%20unemployed%20youth%20have%20been%20registered%20with%20employment%20exchanges%20in%20the%20state%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%20CMIE%2C%20released%20in%20January%20this%20year%2C%20showed%20that%2C%20at%2037.4%20per%20cent%20Haryana%20had%20the%20highest%20unemployment%20rate%20in%20India%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20national%20unemployment%20rate%20of%208.3%20per%20cent.%20Chief%20Minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20of%20the%20BJP%20has%20dismissed%20the%20CMIE%20data%20and%20pointed%20to%20recruitments%20in%20the%20Staff%20Selection%20Commission%20and%20Haryana%20Public%20Service%20Commission%2C%20among%20others%2C%20to%20buttress%20his%20claims%20of%20providing%20employment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20order%20last%20month%2C%20which%20struck%20down%20a%202020%20law%20providing%2075%25%20reservation%20in%20private%20jobs%20to%20residents%20of%20Haryana%2C%20has%20also%20opened%20up%20the%20Khattar%20government%20to%20criticism%20over%20youth%20not%20getting%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Give%20Us%20Jobs%20Here'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20worker%20from%20Kurukshetra%20said%20the%20government%20should%20give%20them%20jobs%20in%20India.%20%26quot%3BIsrael%20is%20involved%20in%20a%20war%2C%20why%20is%20the%20government%20sending%20us%20there%3F%20The%20government%20keeps%20saying%20that%20our%20country%20is%20becoming%20wealthy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chandan%2C%20a%20construction%20worker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20also%20trained%20its%20guns%20on%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20in%20Haryana.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BEveryone%20knows%20Israel%20is%20a%20warzone.%20The%20state%20government%20should%20give%20our%20youth%20jobs%20in%20Haryana%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Congress%20MLA%20Neeraj%20Sharma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernment's%20Take%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20government%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20its%20aim%20was%20to%20prevent%20cheating%20and%20people%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20to%20Israel%20if%20they%20don't%20want%20to.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20unique%20initiative%20by%20the%20government%2C%20which%20will%20ensure%20that%20travel%20agents%20can't%20fleece%20people.%20We%20receive%20complaints%20about%20that%20every%20day.%20There%20is%20no%20compulsion%20to%20go%20to%20Israel%2C%20it's%20only%20for%20people%20who%20want%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Haryana%20Education%20Minister%20Kanwar%20Pal%20Gujjar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20query%20by%20Congress%20MP%20KC%20Venugopal%2C%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20External%20Affairs%20V%20Muraleed