s%2C%20the%20party%20supremo%2C%20who%20is%20eying%20to%20become%20prime%20minister%20for%20a%20record%20fourth%20time%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20he%20was%20ousted%20from%20power%20three%20times%20in%201993%2C%201999%20and%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20where%20Pakistan%20has%20reached%20(in%20terms%20of%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy)%20this%20is%20not%20done%20by%20India%2C%20the%20US%20or%20even%20Afghanistan.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20shot%20ourselves%20in%20our%20own%20foot...they%20(a%20reference%20to%20the%20military)%20imposed%20a%20selected%20(government)%20on%20this%20nation%20by%20rigging%20the%202018%20polls%20that%20led%20to%20the%20sufferings%20of%20the%20people%20and%20downfall%20of%20the%20economy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharif%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2073-year-old%20leader%20castigated%20the%20judges%20for%20legitimising%20military%20dictators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20judges%20garland%20them%20(military%20dictators)%20and%20legitimise%20their%20rule%20when%20they%20break%20the%20Constitution.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20a%20prime%20minister%20the%20judges%20stamp%20his%20ouster.%20The%20judges%20also%20approve%20the%20act%20of%20dissolution%20of%20the%20parliament...why%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20supremo%20lashed%20out%20at%20former%20ISI%20chief%20Gen%20Faiz%20Hamid%20for%20his%20role%20in%20ousting%20him%20from%20power%20in%202017.%20%E2%80%9CA%20case%20has%20been%20opened%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20those%20(Faiz%20Hamid%20and%20others)%20who%20had%20said%20that%20if%20Nawaz%20came%20out%20of%20jail%20their%20two-year%20hard%20work%20would%20be%20wasted%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PML-N%20leader%2C%20who%20returned%20to%20the%20country%20from%20London%20in%20October%20ending%20a%20four-year-long%20self-imposed%20exile%2C%20is%20the%20only%20Pakistani%20politician%20who%20became%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20the%20coup-prone%20c