0headlines%20should%20not%20minimise%20the%20importance%20of%20other%20news.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20General%20M%20M%20Naravane%20has%20disclosed%20in%20his%20memoir%20that%20the%20Agnipath%20or%20Agniveer%20scheme%20came%20as%20a%20total%20surprise%20to%20the%20Army%2C%20Air%20Force%20and%20Navy%20chiefs%2C%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Naravane)%20has%20now%20confirmed%20what%20had%20been%20commonly%20believed%20when%20the%20Agnipath%2FAgniveer%20scheme%20was%20bulldozed%20through%20without%20meaningful%20consultations%20with%20those%20who%20were%20being%20directly%20impacted%20by%20such%20a%20disastrous%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20weeks%20after%20becoming%20the%20Army%20chief%2C%20General%20Naravane%20sounded%20out%20in%20early%202020%20about%20the%20%26quot%3BTour%20of%20Duty%26quot%3B%20scheme%20for%20inducting%20soldiers%20for%20short%20tenures%20but%20months%20later%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%20(PMO)%20came%20up%20with%20a%20formulation%20with%20a%20much%20wider%20scope%20to%20include%20all%20the%20three%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20General%20Naravane%20has%20written%20in%20his%20memoir%2C%20titled%20%26quot%3BFour%20Stars%20of%20Destiny%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20elaborating%20on%20the%20birth%20of%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20--%20considered%20India's%20most%20radical%20military%20recruitment%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20formulation%20of%20the%20new%20scheme%2C%20General%20Naravane%20has%20said%20the%20Army%20was%20%26quot%3Btaken%20by%20surprise%20by%20this%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20but%20for%20the%20Navy%20and%20Air%20Force%2C%20it%20came%20like%20a%20bolt%20from%20the%20blue%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20had%20first%20sounded%20out%20the%20prime%20minister%20about%20the%20Tour%20of%20Duty%20scheme%2C%20it%20was%20more%20on%20