%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106132995.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ECyprus%20disrupts%20Iranian%20plot%20targeting%20Israeli%20businessmen%20with%20the%20arrest%20of%20two%20Iranian%20asylum-seekers%20in%20contact%20with%20a%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20member.%20The%20suspects%20have%20been%20in%20custody%20since%20Nov.%203%20and%20will%20be%20deported.%20The%20operation%20was%20a%20joint%20effort%20with%20Israel's%20Mossad.%20Cypriot%20security%20services%20had%20been%20surveilling%20the%20men%20before%20their%20arrest%2C%20which%20prevented%20a%20potential%20killing.%20The%20targeted%20individuals%20were%20primarily%20Israeli%20businessmen.%20This%20is%20the%20third%20Iranian%20plot%20in%20Cyprus%20in%20over%20a%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fcyprus-says-a-joint-operation-with-mossad-has-foiled-a-suspected-iranian-plot-to-kill-israelis%2Farticleshow%2F106132995.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fcyprus-says-a-joint-operation-with-mossad-has-foiled-a-suspected-iranian-plot-to-kill-israelis%2Famp_articleshow%2F106132995.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fcyprus-says-a-joint-operation-with-mossad-has-foiled-a-suspected-iranian-plot-to-kill-israelis%2Famp_articleshow%2F106132995.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Punjab%20Didn't%20Get%20Health%20Scheme%20Funds%20Over%20Branding%20Guidelines%3A%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20not%20released%20its%20share%20of%20Rs%20402.48%20crore%20under%20the%20National%20Health%20Mission%20to%20Punjab%20due%20to%20the%20state's%20non-compliance%20with%20branding%20guidelines%20for%20Ayushman%20Bharat-Health%20and%20Wellness%20Centres%2C%20the%20government%20told%20Parliament%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20has%20branded%20the%20centres%20as%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Clinic%20(PHC-HWC)%20instead%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat-Health%20and%20Wellness%20Centre%20(now%2C%20Ayushman%20Arogya%20Mandir)%2C%20thereby%20violating%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20pact%20signed%20between%20the%20Union%20Health%20Ministry%20and%20the%20state%2C%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Health%20Bharati%20Pravin%20Pawar%20said%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20has%20also%20not%20followed%20the%20colour%20scheme%2C%20nor%20has%20it%20displayed%20the%20six%20logos%2C%20she%20said%2C%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20reasons%20behind%20not%20releasing%20Rs%20621%20crore%20to%20Punjab%20under%20the%20National%20Health%20Mission%20(NHM).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Pawar%20stated%20that%20the%20Department%20of%20Expenditure%20(DoE)%20guidelines%20stipulate%20that%20all%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%20have%20to%20adhere%20to%20the%20guidelines%20of%20the%20Scheme%20for%20Special%20Assistance%20to%20States%20for%20Capital%20Investment%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20mandatory%20conditions%20stipulates%2C%20%26quot%3BFull%20compliance%20with%20the%20official%20names%20of%20all%20Centrally%20Sponsored%20Schemes%20(CSSs)%20%5Bcorrect%20translation%20to%20local%20language%20is%20permissible%5D%20and%20any%20guidelines%2Finstructions%20issued%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20regarding%20the%20branding%20of%20CSSs%2C%20in%20all%20Schemes%20of%20all%20Ministries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Memorandum%20of%20Understanding%20(MoU)%20was%20signed%20between%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20and%20the%20government%20of%20Punjab%20on%20January%2016%2C%202023%2C%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20National%20Health%20Mission%20(NHM)%20from%20April%201%2C%202021%2C%20to%20March%2031%2C%202026%2C%20Ms%20Pawar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClause%2010.3%20of%20the%20NHM%20specifies%20that%20the%20state%20shall%20ensure%20that%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20programme%20or%20activities%20envisaged%20under%20the%20mission%20is%20as%20per%20the%20framework%20of%20implementation%20of%20the%20NHM%20and%20other%20guidelines%20provided%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClause%2010.10%20of%20the%20NHM%20specifies%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20state%20government%20shall%20adhere%20to%20all%20the%20existing%20manuals%2C%20guidelines%2C%20instructions%20and%20circulars%20issued%20in%20connection%20with%20implementation%20of%20the%20NHM%2C%20which%20are%20not%20contrary%20to%20the%20provisions%20of%20this%20MOU%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetailed%20guidelines%20on%20the%20branding%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat-Health%20and%20Wellness%20Centres%20or%20Ayushman%20Arogya%20Mandir%20were%20issued%20to%20all%20states%20and%20UTs%20on%20May%2030%2C%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompliance%20with%20the%20guidelines%20was%20reviewed%20with%20all%20states%20and%20UTs%20frequently%20in%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20letter%20dated%20November%2025%2C%202023%2C%20was%20also%20shared%20with%20the%20state%20for%20renaming%20the%20AB-HWCs%20as%20Ayushman%20Arogya%20Mandir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Punjab%20government%20has%20not%20adhered%20to%20the%20DoE%20mandatory%20compliance%20guidelines%20on%20the%20scheme...violated%20the%20provisions%20of%20Clause%2010.3%20and%2010.10%20of%20MoU...%20has%20not%20followed%20the%20branding%20guidelines...%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Pawar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20of%20health%20wrote%20several%20letters%20informing%20the%20state%20about%20this%20issue%20and%20a%20review%20meeting%20was%20held%20with%20the%20minister%20of%20health%20of%20Punjab%20in%20New%20Delhi%20under%20the%20chairmanship%20of%20Union%20Health%20Minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20financial%