ion%2F_132087840_p0h0djw2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-67757395%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CCTV%20footage%20shows%20customers%20and%20staff%20pausing%20for%20a%20moment%20before%20scrambling%20for%20the%20exit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A410%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-asia-67757395%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tamil%20Nadu%20Minister%20K%20Ponmudy%20Convicted%20In%20Disproportionate%20Assets%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Madras%20High%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20set%20aside%20an%20order%20of%20a%20trial%20court%2C%20acquitting%20Higher%20Education%20Minister%20and%20DMK%20leader%20K%20Ponmudy%20and%20his%20wife%20P%20Visalakshi%20in%20a%20Rs%201.75%20crore%20disproportionate%20assets%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPassing%20orders%20on%20an%20appeal%20filed%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Vigilance%20and%20Anti-Corruption%2C%20Justice%20G%20Jayachandran%20convicted%20the%20Minister%20and%20his%20wife%20and%20directed%20them%20to%20be%20present%20in%20the%20court%20on%20December%2021%20for%20pronouncing%20the%20sentence%20after%20hearing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20set%20aside%20the%20order%20of%20the%20Principal%20District%20Judge%2C%20Villupuram%2C%20acquitting%20Ponmudy%20and%20his%20wife%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charge%20of%20offence%20punishable%20under%20Section%2013%20(2)%20read%20with%20section%2013%20(1)%20(e)%20of%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%20framed%20against%20Ponmudy%20stands%20proved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20sections%20are%20related%20to%20criminal%20misconduct%20by%20a%20public%20servant%20and%20illicit%20enrichment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charges%20under%20same%20sections%20of%20PC%20Act%20read%20with%20section%20109%20of%20I%20P%20C%20(abetment)%20against%20Visalakshi%20are%20proved%2C%20the%20court%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20pointed%20to%20overwhelming%20evidence%20against%20the%20accused%20and%20the%20unsustainable%20reasons%20given%20by%20the%20trial%20court%20for%20acquittal%20them%20by%20ignoring%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judgment%20of%20the%20trial%20Court%20is%20palpably%20wrong%2C%20manifestly%20erroneous%20and%20demonstrably%20unsustainable.%20%26quot%3BHence%2C%20this%20is%20a%20fit%20case%20for%20the%20Appellate%20Court%20to%20interfere%20and%20set%20it%20aside%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20said%20the%20ready%20acceptance%20of%20Income%20Tax%20returns%20of%20Visalakshi%20by%20the%20trial%20Court%20without%20appreciating%20independent%20evidence%20was%20palpably%20wrong%20and%20manifestly%20erroneous.%20The%20trial%20Court%2C%20before%20jumping%20into%20the%20said%20conclusion%20ought%20to%20have%20searched%20for%20supportive%20and%20independent%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20absence%20of%20independent%20evidence%2C%20accepting%20the%20fanciful%20claim%20of%20agricultural%20income%20to%20a%20tune%20of%20Rs.55%2C36%2C488%2F-%20as%20against%20the%20estimated%20agricultural%20income%20of%20Rs.13%2C81%2C182%2F-%20was%20infirm%20and%20demonstrably%20unsustainable%2C%20the%20judge%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20said%20ignoring%20the%20first%20principle%20of%20law%20and%20the%20judicial%20pronouncements%2C%20acceptance%20of%20the%20'self-serving%20declaration%20of%20income%20to%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Authority%2C%20by%20an%20accused%20in%20a%20disproportionate%20assets%20case%20was%20not%20a%20possible%20view'%20but%20an%20erroneous%20view%20conceived%20due%20to%20misconception.%20It%20was%20a%20conclusion%20arrived%20by%20ignoring%20the%20most%20reliable%20evidence%20let%20in%20by%20the%20prosecution%20regarding%20the%20income%20of%20A-1%20(Ponmudy)%20and%20A-2%20(Visalakshi).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20Judge%20has%20also%20misinterpreted%20bank%20account%20statements%20as%20proof%20of%20income.%20A%20complete%20miscarriage%20of%20justice%20had%20occurred%20by%20the%20omission%20of%20reliable%20evidence%20and%20by%20misinterpretation%20of%20the%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecution%20case%20was%20that%20Ponmudy%20had%20amassed%20wealth%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%201.75%20crore%20in%20his%20name%20and%20in%20the%20name%20of%20his%20wife%2C%20disproportionate%20to%20his%20known%20sources%20of%20income%20when%20he%20was%20a%20Minister%20between%202006%20and%202011%20in%20the%20DMK%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20is%20likely%20to%20face%20disqualification%2C%20which%20will%20be%20clear%20following%20pronouncement%20of%20sentence%20by%20the%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702999260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4u53vab8_k-ponmudy-ed-office-650_625x300_17_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadras-high-court-convicts-tamil-nadu-minister-k-ponmudy-his-wife-p-visalakshi-in-disproportionate-assets-case-4704865%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Madras%20High%20Court%20Justice%20G%20Jayachandran%20convicted%20the%20Minister%20and%20his%20wife%20and%20directed%20them%20to%20be%20present%20in%20the%20court%20on%20December%2021%20for%20pronouncing%20the%20sentence%20after%20hearing%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadras-high-court-convicts-tamil-nadu-minister-k-ponmudy-his-wife-p-visalakshi-in-disproportionate-assets-case-4704865%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadras-high-court-convicts-tamil-nadu-minister-k-ponmudy-his-wife-p-visalakshi-in-disproportionate-assets-case-4704865%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadras-high-court-convicts-tamil-nadu-minister-k-ponmudy-his-wife-p-visalakshi-in-disproportionate-assets-case-4704865%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Union%20Health%20Ministry%20Writes%20to%20States%20Over%20New%20COVID-19%20Variant%2C%20Asks%20to%20Amp%20up%20Surveillance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19131634%2FScreenshot-2023-12-19-at-1.16.08-PM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20response%20to%20the%20recent%20surge%20in%20COVID-19%20cases%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20detection%20of%20the%20first%20case%20of%20the%20new%20JN.1%20variant%20of%20the%20virus%2C%20the%20Union%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1987840%5C%22%3Ehealth%20ministry%20has%20issued%20a%20directive%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20all%20states%20and%20union%20territories%20(UTs)%20to%20monitor%20the%20situation%20closely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1987840%5C%22%3Eletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20addressed%20to%20them%2C%20the%20ministry%20has%20asked%20states%20to%20monitor%20cases%20of%20influenza-like%20illnesses%20(ILI)%2C%20conduct%20adequate%20testing%2C%20and%20send%20all%20positive%20samples%20for%20whole%20genome%20sequencing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20said%20that%20as%20the%20COVID-19%20virus%20continues%20to%20circulate%20and%20its%20behaviour%20adapts%20to%20Indian%20weather%20conditions%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20to%20uphold%20the%20momentum%20in%20addressing%20public%20health%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20came%20after%20at%20least%20one%20case%20of%20the%20new%20variant%20JN.1%20was%20detected%20during%20routine%20surveillance%20in%20Kerala.%20The%20variant%20was%20also%20detected%20in%20the%20sample%20of%20a%20traveller%20from%20Singapore%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20Tiruchirapalli%2C%20according%20to%20the%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20we%20know%20about%20the%20new%20variant%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sub-variant%20JN.1%20is%20a%20descendant%20of%20the%20BA.2.86%20variant%2C%20commonly%20referred%20to%20as%20Pirola%2C%20and%20is%20not%20exactly%20new.%20The%20first%20cases%20of%20this%20variant%20were%20detected%20in%20the%20United%20States%20in%20September%20and%20the%20first%20case%20globally%20was%20detected%20as%20early%20as%20January%20this%20year%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-health%2Fcentre-writes-to-states-over-new-covid-variant-all-you-should-know-about-jn-1-9073584%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvidence%2C%20so%20far%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20suggest%20that%20JN.1%20can%20cause%20worse%20symptoms%20or%20spread%20faster%20than%20the%20variants%20already%20in%20circulation.%20There%20were%20concerns%20that%20the%20high%20number%20of%20mutations%20could%20mean%20that%20Pirola%20would%20evade%20immune%20response%20more%20easily%20and%20spread%20rapidly%20but%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20happen%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-health%2Fcentre-writes-to-states-over-new-covid-variant-all-you-should-know-about-jn-1-9073584%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20an%20assessment%20by%20the%20WHO%20Technical%20Advisory%20Group%20on%20COVID-19%20Vaccine%20Composition%20showed%20that%20Pirola%20and%20JN.1%20were%20both%20effectively%20neutralised%20by%20serum%20from%20humans%20who%20had%20had%20the%20infection%20and%20vaccination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrategies%20outlined%20by%20the%20ministry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20health%20secretary%20outlined%20key%20strategies%20for%20COVID%20control%20and%20management%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStates%20have%20been%20advised%20to%20implement%20necessary%20public%20health%20measures%20to%20minimise%20the%20risk%20of%20increased%20disease%20transmission%20ahead%20of%20the%20upcoming%20festive%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20complying%20with%20the%20revised%20surveillance%20strategy%20for%20COVID-19%20provided%20by%20the%20Union%20health%20ministry%2C%20states%20have%20been%20asked%20monitor%20and%20report%20Influenza-like%20Illness%20(ILI)%20and%20severe%20acute%20respiratory%20illness%20(SARI)%20cases%20on%20a%20district-wise%20basis%20and%20regularly%20update%20the%20Integrated%20Health%20Information%20Platform%20(IHIP)%20portal%20to%20detect%20early%20rising%20trends%20in%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20also%20asked%20the%20states%20to%20promote%20community%20awareness%20and%20emphasise%20adherence%20to%20respiratory%20hygiene%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702998975000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19131634%2FScreenshot-2023-12-19-at-1.16.08-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Funion-health-ministry-writes-to-states-over-new-covid-19-variant-asks-to-amp-up-surveillance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Evidence%2C%20so%20far%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20suggest%20that%20JN.1%20can%20cause%20worse%20symptoms%20or%20spread%20faster%20than%20the%20variants%20already%20in%20circulation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Funion-health-ministry-writes-to-states-over-new-covid-19-variant-asks-to-amp-up-surveillance%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20it%20still%20safe%20to%20go%20to%20Iceland%20and%20will%20volcanic%20eruption%20disrupt%20European%20flights%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702998540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2Fs