ing%20a%20prominent%20Dalit%20face%20in%20the%20Opposition%2C%20the%20plan%20got%20widespread%20approval.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwelve%20of%20the%20participating%20parties%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20applauded%20the%20plan.%20Even%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20--%20known%20for%20being%20mostly%20out-of-sync%20with%20the%20Congress%20--%20seconded%20the%20idea.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20chance%20to%20have%20the%20country's%20first%20Dalit%20Prime%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20sources%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%2C%20however%2C%20poured%20cold%20water%20on%20the%20plan%20with%20a%20polite%20refusal%2C%20sources%20said.%20He%20said%20he%20only%20wants%20to%20work%20for%20the%20downtrodden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20win%20first%2C%20and%20think%20what%20to%20do%20to%20win.%20What%20is%20the%20point%20in%20discussing%20PM%20before%20having%20MPs.%20We%20will%20try%20to%20get%20a%20majority%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%C2%A0%20later%20told%20reporters%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20faced%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20for%20fielding%20candidates%20against%20Ramnath%20Kovind%20and%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20--%20members%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Tribes%20--%20during%20the%20Presidential%20elections.%20The%20BJP%20has%20accused%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20other%20parties%20of%20being%20biased%20against%20Dalits%20and%20tribals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wide%20approval%20of%20Mr%20Kharge%20is%20also%20seen%20as%20an%20indication%20of%20his%20stature%20among%20the%20Opposition%20parties.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20snub%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20over%20whose%20candidature%20for%20the%20top%20post%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20always%20been%20divided.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20reporters%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20the%20contentious%20issue%20of%20seat%20sharing%20will%20be%20handled%20at%20the%20state%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20any%20issue%2C%20it%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20at%20Central%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20several%20other%20parties%20have%20decided%20on%20December%2031%20as%20the%20deadline%20for%20seat-sharing%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E28%20parties%20had%20taken%20part%20in%20today's%20mega%20meet%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20many%20in%20the%20days%20to%20come.%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20they%20would%20hold%20multiple%20meets%20across%20various%20cities.%20%26quot%3BUnless%20we%20do%20that%20we%20cannot%20raise%20people's%20awareness%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702992840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fgmj2lekk_kharge-rahul-1200_625x300_16_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-proposes-mallikarjun-kharge-as-india-blocs-pm-face-sources-4703787%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20--%20who%20declared%20yesterday%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20not%20take%20a%20call%20on%20its%20Prime%20Ministerial%20candidate%20until%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20--%20took%20a%20180-degree%20turn%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A55%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-proposes-mallikarjun-kharge-as-india-blocs-pm-face-sources-4703787%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-proposes-mallikarjun-kharge-as-india-blocs-pm-face-sources-4703787%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-proposes-mallikarjun-kharge-as-india-blocs-pm-face-sources-4703787%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vedanta%20board