20minister%2C%20in%20complete%20contrast%20to%20his%20predecessor%2C%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20(KCR)%2C%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20being%20inaccessible.%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20occupy%20the%20palatial%20official%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20bungalow%2C%20his%20decision%20to%20throw%20open%20the%20state%20secretariat%20to%20common%20people%2C%20his%20decision%20to%20re-institute%20Praja%20Darbar%20(a%20grievance%20redressal%20mechanism)%2C%20and%20his%20austerity%20measures%20have%20won%20him%20praise%20from%20several%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20refused%20to%20let%20the%20police%20purchase%20new%20high-end%20cars%20for%20his%20convoy%20%E2%80%93%20a%20practice%20familiar%20whenever%20the%20government%20or%20chief%20minister%20changes.%20He%20not%20only%20retained%20the%20old%20cars%20(used%20by%20his%20predecessors)%20but%20pruned%20their%20number%20from%2015%20to%20nine.%20He%2C%20however%2C%20agreed%20to%20give%20the%20cars%20fresh%20paint%20in%20a%20different%20colour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftelangana-revanth-reddy-fortified-pragati-bhavan-open-to-public%5C%22%3ETelangana%3A%20As%20Revanth%20Takes%20Over%2C%20Once-Fortified%20Official%20Residence%20of%20CM%20Thrown%20Open%20to%20Public%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)-led%20opposition%20has%20denied%20any%20refreshing%20style%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20or%20the%20new%20government%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20party.%20Former%20finance%20minister%20and%20BRS%20MLA%20T.%20Harish%20Rao%20said%20Reddy%20still%20spoke%20like%20an%20opposition%20leader%20rather%20than%20as%20a%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao%20asked%20Reddy%20to%20prove%20his%20credentials%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20instead%20of%20blaming%20the%20previous%20government%20all%20the%20time.%20According%20to%20Rao%2C%20Reddy%20relies%20on%20%E2%80%9Cfake%20news%E2%80%9D%20circulated%20on%20social%20media.%20He%20also%20alleged%20that%20Reddy%20on%20the%20very%20second%20day%20of%20assuming%20office%20had%20unleashed%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfalse%20campaign%E2%80%9D%20on%20social%20media%20noting%20that%20he%20inherited%20huge%20debt%20from%20the%20previous%20BRS%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20taking%20oath%20as%20chief%20minister%20on%20December%207%2C%20Reddy%20handed%20over%20an%20appointment%20letter%20to%20T.%20Rajini%20on%20the%20same%20stage%20at%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Stadium%20in%20Hyderabad.%20A%20post-graduate%20in%20commerce%20from%20Osmania%20University%2C%20Rajini%20impressed%20Reddy%20with%20her%20articulation%20when%20she%20met%20him%20at%20the%20Congress%20party%20office%20three%20months%20ago.%20He%20had%20assured%20her%20that%20he%20would%20sign%20her%20appointment%20letter%20as%20the%20first%20file%20immediately%20after%20taking%20over%20as%20chief%20minister.%20Rajini%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20a%20project%20manager%20in%20Telangana%20State%20Seed%20and%20Organic%20Certification%20Agency%20with%20a%20monthly%20salary%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%2C%20but%20on%20a%20contract%20basis%20until%20her%20service%20is%20regularised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19175635%2FGAwjl8VWkAEFtit.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19175635%2FGAwjl8VWkAEFtit.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19175635%2FGAwjl8VWkAEFtit-300x167.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19175635%2FGAwjl8VWkAEFtit-1024x570.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689881%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22668%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERevanth%20Reddy%20signs%20the%20appointment%20letter%20of%20Rajini.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40TelanganaCMO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddy%20came%20in%20for%20praise%20even%20in%20official%20circles%20for%20displaying%20%E2%80%9Cmaturity%E2%80%9D%20than%20previous%20chief%20ministers%20though%20he%20was%20not%20even%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20past.%20He%20began%20his%20political%20career%20as%20a%20territorial%20constituency%20member%20of%20a%20local%20body%2C%20served%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20legislative%20council%20(MLC)%20for%20a%20brief%2C%20and%20MLA%20twice.%20In%20his%20second%20term%20as%20MLA%2C%20he%20was%20often%20suspended%20from%20the%20Assembly%20or%20shouted%20down%20by%20treasury%20benches%20representing%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20winning%20praise%20for%20handling%20legislative%20debates%20in%20the%20face%20of%20scathing%20attacks%20from%20BRS%20legislators.%20In%20the%20nearly%20two-hour%20speech%20that%20was%20live%20telecast%20as%20part%20of%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20motion%20of%20thanks%20to%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20address%2C%20he%20said%20his%20narrative%20was%20as%20good%20as%20punishment%20to%20the%20BRS%20leaders%20for%20their%20wrongdoing.%20He%20said%20his%20government%20would%20not%20press%20for%20their%20suspension%20for%20their%20unruly%20behaviour%20but%20would%20force%20them%20to%20listen%20to%20him%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20process%2C%20he%20dug%20into%20the%20sale%20of%20paddy%20seed%20grown%20by%20KCR%20in%20his%20150%20acres%20of%20crop%20to%20seed%20companies%20at%20Rs%204%2C250%20a%20quintal%20while%20other%20farmers%20got%20only%20Rs%201%2C900%20a%20quintal.%20He%20walked%20away%20with%20the%20credit%20of%20implementing%20two%20of%20the%20six%20guarantees%20of%20Congress%20immediately%20after%20taking%20over.%20They%20relate%20to%20free%20bus%20travel%20for%20women%20and%20a%20hike%20in%20the%20ceiling%20of%20cashless%20treatment%20under%20the%20Aarogyasri%20scheme%20for%20the%20poor%20in%20corporate%20hospitals%20from%20Rs%205%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarish%20Rao%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20not%20six%20but%2013%20guarantees%20which%20Congress%20gave%20and%20only%20two%20were%20delivered.%20Rao%20said%20the%20guarantee%20on%20health%20was%20not%20new%20because%20the%20previous%20BRS%20government%20had%20permitted%20organ%20transplants%20costing%20up%20to%20Rs%2011%20lakh%20for%20the%20poor%20at%20private%20hospitals%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddy%20ordered%20the%20removal%20of%20barricades%20at%20the%20premises%20hitherto%20occupied%20by%20KCR%20to%20make%20it%20accessible%20to%20the%20public%20for%20giving%20representations%20on%20public%20grievances%20redressal%20days.%20He%20has%20announced%20a%20judicial%20inquiry%20into%20question%20papers%20leak%20in%20recruitment%20exams%20and%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Kaleswaram%20lift-irrigation%20project%20which%20was%20hit%20by%20the%20sinking%20of%20a%20pier%20of%20one%20of%20its%20three%20barrages.%20He%20has%20also%20stopped%20the%20extension%20of%20Hyderabad%20metro%20rail%20works%20from%20Raidurg%20to%20the%20international%20airport%20following%20complaints%20that%20the%20work%20was%20commissioned%20to%20benefit%20a%20few%20landowners%20with%20close%20links%20in%20the%20previous%20BRS%20government.%20Instead%2C%20the%20route%20was%20ordered%20to%20be%20realigned%20from%20the%20Old%20City%20to%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevanth%20Reddy%20was%20firm%20on%20the%20replacement%20of%20the%20Dharani%20portal%20of%20land%20transactions%20which%20was%20introduced%20by%20the%20BRS%20government%20three%20years%20ago.%20This%20was%20because%20of%20lakhs%20of%20complaints%20by%20the%20public%20about%20illegal%20transactions%20that%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20eased%20out%20a%20dozen%20retired%20bureaucrats%20who%20were%20employed%20as%20advisors%20to%20the%20government%20and%20effected%20major%20changes%20in%20the%20top%20brass%20of%20IAS%20and%20IPS.%20He%20also%20stripped%20the%20chairpersons%20of%20a%20dozen%20corporations%20of%20their%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wanted%20a%20delegation%20to%20visit%20Bengaluru%20to%20discuss%20the%20release%20of%20water%20by%20Karnataka%20from%20the%20Narayanpur%20dam%20to%20meet%20the%20drinking%20water%20requirement%20of%20Telangana%20in%20the%20Krishna%20basin.%20He%20strengthened%20the%20Telangana%20State%20Anti-Narcotics%20Bureau%20by%20appointing%20a%20full-time%20director%20and%20sanctioning%20300%20staff%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20a%20meeting%20with%20former%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20governor%20Raghuram%20Rajan%20to%20discuss%20measures%20to%20put%20the%20economy%20of%20the%20state%20back%20on%20the%20rails%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20outstanding%20loans%20touching%20Rs%203.66%20lakh%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20department%20was%20asked%20to%20prepare%20a%20White%20Paper%20on%20the%20economy%20to%20be%20tabled%20in%20the%20assembly%20on%20Wednesday.%20On%20his%20instructions%2C%20the%20government%20machinery%20is%20gearing%20up%20to%20resume%20distribution%20of%20ration%20cards%20for%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20inclusion%20of%20new%20names%20at%20gram%20sabhas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20analyst%20K.%20Nageshwar%20said%20the%20optics%20of%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20government%20have%20been%20fairly%20good%20so%20far.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20opening%20the%20gates%20of%20the%20Secretariat%20to%20the%20public%2C%20holding%20Praja%20Darbar%20to%20hear%20public%20grievances%2C%20and%20resuming%20permissions%20for%20protests%20at%20Dharna%20Chowk%20near%20Indira%20Park%2C%20Reddy%20has%20shown%20his%20liberal%20and%20democratic%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Nageshwar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20Jana%20Samithi%20chief%20M.%20Kodandaram%20said%20the%20days%20of%20%E2%80%9Cwarm%20and%20friend