%80%99s%20first-innings%20bowling%20figures%20of%205-7%20are%20now%20part%20of%20Indian%20cricket%20folklore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20another%20reason%20for%20Deepti%20and%20her%20teammates%20to%20treasure%20this%20win%20%E2%80%93%20Test%20matches%20are%20rare%20in%20the%20career%20of%20an%20Indian%20woman%20cricketer.%20In%20the%20last%2020%20years%2C%20the%20Indian%20women%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20team%20has%20played%20just%20ten%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20just%20for%20comparison%2C%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%20the%20Indian%20men%E2%80%99s%20team%20has%20played%2095%20matches!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20women%20are%20ready%20to%20play%2C%20the%C2%A0BCCI%C2%A0is%20not%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20a%20complete%20travesty.%20So%20much%20cricketing%20talent%20is%20shut%20out%20because%20the%20game%20is%20run%20by%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20cricket%20fans%2C%20it%20has%20been%20frustrating%20to%20see%20players%20like%20Mithali%20Raj%2C%20Jhulan%20Goswami%20and%2C%20more%20recently%2C%20the%20precocious%20young%20cricketers%20like%20Harmanpreet%20Kaur%2C%20Smriti%20Mandhana%2C%20Shefali%20Verma%2C%20Deepti%20Sharma%20and%20Jemima%20Rodrigues%20sit%20out%20for%20months%20despite%20being%20hungry%20to%20play%2C%20despite%20being%20in%20the%20prime%20of%20their%20lives%2C%20despite%20being%20at%20the%20top%20of%20their%20form%20and%20skill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20even%20more%20inexcusable%20because%20today%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwomens-cricket-is-rife-with-stories-of-sexual-harassment-what-is-the-bcci-doing%5C%22%3EBoard%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20one%20of%20the%20richest%20sports%20bodies%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20money%2C%20the%20resources%2C%20the%20stadiums%2C%20the%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20talent%2C%20the%20fans%2C%20the%20sponsor%20interest%2C%20the%20appetite%20%E2%80%93%20all%20of%20it%20is%20there%2C%20but%20the%20men%20in%20charge%20have%20been%20dragging%20their%20feet.%20For%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECounter-arguments%20will%20be%20trotted%20out.%20For%20instance%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98Test%20cricket%20is%20dying%2C%20so%20we%20have%20focused%20on%20ODI%20and%20T20%20international%20(T20I)%20cricket%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20women%E2%80%99.%20Or%2C%20%E2%80%98it%20is%20also%20tougher%20to%20market%20women%E2%80%99s%20Test%20matches%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19165425%2FIndia-test-team-1024x683.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19165425%2FIndia-test-team-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19165425%2FIndia-test-team-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19165425%2FIndia-test-team.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689856%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20men%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20team%20has%20played%2095%20Test%20matches%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%20and%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20team%E2%80%99s%20has%20played%20ten%20matches%20in%20the%20last%2020%20years.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40BCCI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%93%20if%20Test%20cricket%20is%20dying%20and%20hard%20to%20sell%2C%20then%20why%20are%20the%20men%20playing%20it%3F%20Because%20it%20is%20still%20the%20purest%20form%20of%20the%20game%2C%20the%20ultimate%20test%20of%20every%20aspect%20of%20cricketing%20skill.%20Why%20should%20India%E2%80%99s%20women%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20fanatics%20be%20kept%20away%20from%20tha