than%20the%20women%20and%20they%20play%20a%20longer%20IPL%20than%20the%20women%20too.%20Can%20the%C2%A0BCCI%C2%A0tell%20us%20why%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19171413%2FWomens-IPL.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19171413%2FWomens-IPL.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19171413%2FWomens-IPL-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689864%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20women%20play%20a%20shorter%20IPL%20than%20the%20men.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40wplt20.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%20male%20chieftains%20should%20either%20put%20away%20their%20male%20egos%20and%20give%20our%20women%20cricketers%20their%20due%2C%20or%20they%20should%20make%20way%20for%20more%20women%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20administration%3B%20not%20just%20at%20the%20top%2C%20but%20at%20the%20state%20and%20district%20levels%20as%20well.%20It%20has%20been%20a%20stag%20party%20for%20far%20too%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPay%20parity%3F%20Not%20really%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJayShah%2Fstatus%2F1585527306352676865%5C%22%3Ethe%C2%A0BCCI%C2%A0announced%20%E2%80%98equal%20match%20fees%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20men%20and%20women%20team%20members%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0Rs%2015%20lakh%20per%20Test%2C%20Rs%206%20lakh%20per%20ODI%20and%20Rs%203%20lakh%20per%20T20I.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%C2%A0positive%20step%2C%20but%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20fully%20address%20the%20gender%20disparity.%20First%2C%20because%2C%20as%20we%20have%20seen%2C%20the%20women%20play%20far%20fewer%20matches%2C%20especially%20Tests%2C%20for%20which%20the%20fees%20are%20highest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20gender%20parity%20is%20still%20not%20being%20applied%20to%20the%20players%E2%80%99%20annual%20contracts.%20And%20here%2C%20the%20disparity%20is%20embarrassingly%20vast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20this%20better%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20Deepti%20Sharma.%20She%20is%20a%20Grade%20A%20player%20%E2%80%93%20the%20highest%20grade%20for%20women%20players%20%E2%80%93%20along%20with%20Harmanpreet%20Kaur%20and%20Smriti%20Mandhana.%20Her%20annual%20contract%20salary%20is%20Rs%2050%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%E2%80%99s%20the%20Grade%20A%2B%20contract%20amount%20for%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%3F%20A%20whopping%20Rs%207%20crore!%20And%20%3Cem%3Ethat%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20gender%20disparity.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20contract%20amount%20for%20Grade%20C%20male%20players%2C%20the%20lowest%20grade%2C%20is%20Rs%201%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20mean%20any%20disrespect%20towards%20Deepak%20Hooda%20%E2%80%93%20he%20is%20a%20sincere%2C%20talented%20cricketer%20and%20has%20played%20a%20bit%20for%20India%2C%20but%20should%20his%20contracted%20salary%20be%20double%20that%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20women%E2%80%99s%20team%20captain%3F%20How%20is%20that%20fair%20or%20justifiable%20in%20any%20manner%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurely%20the%C2%A0BCCI%C2%A0is%20aware%20of%20this%20disparity%2C%20but%20do%20they%20have%20any%20plans%20to%20set%20it%20right%3F%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fsohini-chattopadhyay-the-day-i-became-a-runner-book-review%5C%22%3ECan%20the%20Indian%20Sportswoman%20Speak%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFans%20embrace%20women%E2%80%99s%20cricket%2C%20why%20is%C2%A0the%20BCCI%C2%A0shy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20just%20FYI%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20sheer%20popularity%20amongst%20the%20fans%2C%20to%20understand%20how%20the%20women%20have%20really%20caught%20up%20with%20the%20men%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20a%20good%20metric%20%E2%80%93%20on%20Instagram%2C%20Jadeja%2C%20who%20is%20quite%20a%20darling%20of%20the%20fans%20%E2%80%93%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Sir%20Jadeja%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Jaddu%E2%80%99%20and%20with%20his%20signature%20%E2%80%98bat%20as%20%3Cem%3Etalwaar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20celebration%20after%20every%20big%20innings%20%E2%80%93%20has%207.6%20million%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Smriti%20Mandhana%2C%20currently%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20woman%20batter%2C%20has%208.6%20million%20followers!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20fans%20have%20fully%20acknowledged%20and%20embraced%20women%E2%80%99s%20cricket%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%C2%A0the%20BCCI%C2%A0that%E2%80%99s%20lagging%20behind%20in%20giving%20them%20the%20respect%20and%20space%20they%20deserve%20and%20are%20due.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERemember%20Mithali%20Raj%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWay%20back%20in%201999%2C%20Mithali%20Raj%2C%20then%20just%2016%20years%20old%2C%20made%20an%20astonishing%20start%20to%20her%20international%20cricket%20career%2C%20scoring%20114%20against%20Ireland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20when%C2%A0the%20BCCI%C2%A0should%20have%20taken%20note%20of%20her%20and%20of%20the%20rising%20tide%20of%20female%20cricketing%20talent%20in%20the%20country.%20But%20it%20did%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19172658%2FMithali-Raj-300x300.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19172658%2FMithali-Raj-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fupload