20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20for%20a%20massive%20amount%20of%20Rs%C2%A08.4%20crore.%20Both%20cricketers%20come%20with%20proven%20track%20records%20in%20the%20domestic%20circuit%20and%20their%20performances%20as%20a%20finisher%20made%20them%20attractive%20commodities%20for%20the%20franchises.%20While%20Dubey%20plays%20for%20Vidarbha%20in%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20Rizvi%20plays%20for%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubey%20impressed%20everyone%20with%20his%20explosive%20batting%20performances%20at%20the%20Syed%20Mushtaq%20Ali%20Trophy%20where%20he%20scored%20221%20runs%20in%20seven%20innings%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20187.28.%20He%20played%20an%20integral%20role%20in%20Vidarbha's%20record%20run-chase%20against%20Bengal%20where%20he%20came%20out%20to%20bat%20as%20an%20Impact%20Player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChasing%20a%20target%20of%20213%2C%20he%20scored%20an%20unbeaten%2058%20off%20just%2020%20deliveries%20to%20clinch%20the%20encounter%20with%2013%20balls%20to%20spare.%20The%20innings%2C%20which%20had%203%20fours%20and%206%20sixes%2C%20was%20lauded%20by%20experts%20and%20fans%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Rizvi%20ended%20up%20hitting%20the%20most%20number%20of%20sixes%20for%20Kanpur%20Superstars%20at%20the%20UP%20T20%20League.%20He%20scored%20455%20runs%20in%20the%20competition%20with%20two%20explosive%20hundreds.%20The%20performance%20earned%20him%20trials%20with%20multiple%20IPL%20franchises%20but%20he%20chose%20to%20play%20for%20the%20U-23%20UP%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERizvi%20was%20among%20the%20top%2010%20six-hitters%20in%20the%20Syed%20Mushtaq%20Ali%20T20%20Trophy%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20139.89.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%C2%A0Mitchell%C2%A0Starc%C2%A0surpassed%20his%20Australian%20bowling%20partner%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pat%20Cummins%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1656-pat-cummins-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPat%20Cummins%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20become%20the%20most%20expensive%20buy%20in%20IPL%20history%20with%20an%20eye%20popping%20bid%20of%20Rs%2024.75%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20long%20after%20Cummins%20fetched%20an%20unprecedented%20pay%20packet%20of%2020.50%20crore%20from%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%2C%C2%A0Starc%C2%A0raised%20the%20bar%20when%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20made%20a%20multi%20million%20dollar%20bid%20for%20the%20left-arm%20pacer%20who%20last%20played%20in%20the%20IPL%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20are%20the%20unpredictable%20ways%20of%20IPL%20that%20the%20one%20third%20of%20the%20formidable%20Australian%20pace%20trio%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Josh%20Hazlewood%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1040-josh-hazlewood-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJosh%20Hazlewood%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20went%20unsold%20in%20the%20first%20round%20of%20auction%20from%20a%20base%20price%20of%20Rs%202%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat%20Titans%20and%20KKR%20were%20involved%20in%20a%20long%20and%20exhilarating%20bidding%20battle%20for%C2%A0Starc%C2%A0before%20the%20latter%20lapped%20him%20up%20for%20a%20record%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarc%2C%2033%2C%20has%20usually%20prioritised%20international%20duty%20over%20IPL%20but%20decided%20to%20enter%20the%20auction%20with%20one%20eye%20on%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20that%20follows%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20only%20played%20only%20two%20seasons%20of%20the%20IPL%2C%20taking%2034%20wickets%20in%2027%20games%20at%20an%20average%20of%2020.38.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20Cummins%20has%20been%20a%20regular%20at%20the%20IPL%20but%20skipped%20the%202023%20edition%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20Ashes%20and%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20intense%20bidding%20war%20followed%20for%20Cummins%20with%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore%2C%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%2C%20and%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20raising%20their%20paddles%20frenetically%20to%20secure%20the%20services%20of%20the%20fast%20bowling%20all-rounder.%3