ttps%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fgermanys-top-court-orders-a-repeat-of-the-2021-national-election-in-parts-of-berlin-due-to-glitches%2Farticleshow%2F106125566.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fgermanys-top-court-orders-a-repeat-of-the-2021-national-election-in-parts-of-berlin-due-to-glitches%2Famp_articleshow%2F106125566.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fgermanys-top-court-orders-a-repeat-of-the-2021-national-election-in-parts-of-berlin-due-to-glitches%2Famp_articleshow%2F106125566.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mayawati%20Names%20Successor%3A%20Contrasting%20Challenges%20Before%20Akash%20Anand%20and%20Chirag%20Paswan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19143324%2FEffect-32.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EMayawati%20has%20anointed%20her%20nephew%20Akash%20Anand%20as%20her%20political%20successor%20to%20help%20expand%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20beyond%20its%20home%20turf%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Tech-savvy%20Anand%20is%20a%20management%20graduate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%2C%20Anand%20has%20risen%20to%20the%20top%20of%20his%20party%20but%20faces%20challenges%20carrying%20forward%20the%20legacy%20he%20has%20been%20handed.%20While%20Paswan%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Anand%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20have%20assumed%20the%20leadership%20of%20their%20respective%20parties%2C%20the%20question%20remains%20if%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20keep%20Dalit%20communities%20united%20in%20contemporary%20politics%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP%20emerged%20as%20the%20most%20potent%20vehicle%20of%20the%20Dalit%20movement%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20the%201990s.%20The%20credit%20goes%20to%20Kanshi%20Ram%20for%20binding%20the%20communities%20into%20a%20distinctly%20robust%20political%20force%20in%20the%20maze%20of%20the%20Hindutva%2C%20centrist%2C%20and%20socialist%20forces%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20populous%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Kanshi%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20stewardship%2C%20the%20BSP%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20of%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20trumped%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%201993%20within%20a%20year%20of%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20December%201992.%20The%20SP-BSP%20alliance%20didn%E2%80%99t%20last%20that%20long.%20The%20BSP%20withdrew%20its%20support%20to%20the%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20government%20in%201995%2C%20but%20the%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20support%20base%20surged%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20populous%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmayawati-bsp-dalit-votes-india-nda%5C%22%3ENeither%20Here%20Nor%20There%3A%20Why%20Mayawati%20Is%20Losing%20Relevance%20in%20the%20Heartland%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20Kanshi%20Ram%20nominated%20Mayawati%20as%20his%20successor.%20%E2%80%9CBehenji%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20she%20is%20referred%20to%20fondly%20by%20her%20cadre%2C%20did%20reasonably%20well%20expanding%20the%20support%20base%20of%20the%20party%2C%20which%20won%20the%202007%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20on%20its%20own.%20She%20completed%20her%20full%20five-year%20tenure%20as%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20probably%2C%20it%20was%20in%20this%20period%20that%20Mayawati%20drifted%20away%20from%20the%20path%20of%20her%20mentor%20and%20the%20most%20profound%20icon%20of%20the%20Dalit%20movement%20in%20post-independent%20India%2C%20Kanshi%20Ram.%20He%20had%20selected%20Mayawati%20%E2%80%93%20the%20talented%20daughter%20of%20a%20post%20office%20employee%20from%20the%20Jatav%20caste%2C%20Prabhu%20Das%20%E2%80%93%20and%20groomed%20her%20for%20a%20leadership%20role%20in%20the%20Dalit%20movement%20that%20he%20had%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanshi%20Ram%20had%20the%20acumen%20to%20build%20the%20second%20rung%20of%20leadership%20in%20his%20lifetime.%20Apart%20from%20catapulting%20Mayawati%20into%20the%20vanguard%20of%20the%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20leadership%2C%20Ram%20also%20incubated%20Sone%20Lal%20Patel%2C%20R.K.%20Choudhary%2C%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%2C%20Sanjay%20Nishad%2C%20and%20several%20others%20to%20make%20the%20BSP%20a%20vehicle%20of%20%E2%80%98collective%20leadership%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F29134513%2FMayawati-and-Kanshi-Ram.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F29134513%2FMayawati-and-Kanshi-Ram.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F29134513%2FMayawati-and-Kanshi-Ram-300x202.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360037%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22431%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMayawati%20with%20BSP%20founder%20Kanshi%20Ram.%20Credit%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20unlike%20Kanshi%20Ram%2C%20Mayawati%20never%20allowed%20the%20second-rung%20leaders%20to%20grow%2C%20and%20in%20the%20process%2C%20she%20slowly%20but%20steadily%20alienated%20several%20Dalit%20communities.%20Prominent%20leaders%20who%20enjoyed%20their%20space%20in%20the%20party%20during%20the%20period%20of%20Kanshi%20Ram%20either%20left%20the%20party%20or%20were%20expelled%20by%20Mayawati.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20Mayawati%E2%80%99s%20support%20base%20shrunk%20to%20the%20Jatav%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%2C%20when%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%20was%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20of%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20he%20openly%20alleged%20that%20Mayawati%20only%20patronised%20the%20Jatavs%20in%20the%20BSP%3B%20others%20had%20no%20place%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20way%2C%20Mayawati%20adopted%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctraits%E2%80%9D%20of%20what%20she%20described%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CManuvadi%20forces%E2%80%9D%2C%20by%20acting%20undemocratically%20and%20suppressing%20the%20voices%20of%20dissent%20in%20her%20party.%20She%20acted%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20she%20was%20perceived%20to%20be%20opposed%20to%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20SP%20and%20supportive%20of%20the%20BJP.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20she%20also%20alienated%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20non-Jatav%20Dalit%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20party%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20has%20continuously%20plummeted%20from%202012%20onwards.%20BSP%20secured%2019.3%25%20votes%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20when%20it%20contested%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20SP.%20That%20declined%20to%2012.88%25%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%2C%20when%20the%20BSP%20contested%20alone%20but%20was%20perceived%20to%20have%20%E2%80%9Chelped%E2%80%9D%20the%20BJP%20by%20pitting%20Muslim%20candidates%20against%20the%20SP%E2%80%99s%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20exploiting%20the%20cracks%20in%20the%20BSP%2C%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20equipped%20with%20a%20better%20organisation%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%20and%20armed%20with%20welfare%20schemes%20for%20the%20poor%20%E2%80%93%20co-opted%20several%20former%20BSP%20leaders%20and%20made%20inroads%20into%20the%20Balmiki%20and%20other%20non-Jatav%20Dalit%20votes%20in%20the%20heartland%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAkash%20Anand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkash%20Anand%20made%20his%20political%20debut%20at%20a%20BSP%20rally%20in%202017.%20With%20the%20%E2%80%98blessings%E2%80%99%20of%20Mayawati%2C%20he%20managed%20the%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20He%20also%20undertook%20a%2013-kilometre%20%E2%80%98Swabhiman%20Yatra%E2%80%99%20through%20various%20Dalit%20settlements%20on%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20in%20Rajasthan%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20fair%20to%20him%2C%20he%20is%20young%2C%20energetic%2C%20educated%2C%20and%20poised%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20new%20generation%20of%20Dalit%20voters.%20But%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20Aazad%20is%20emerging%20as%20a%20new%20leader%20of%20Dalits%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Only%20time%20will%20tell%20if%20Anand%20can%20carry%20forward%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20Dalit%20movement.%20The%20BJP%2C%20SP%2C%20and%20Congress%20may%20want%20to%20share%20the%20%E2%80%9Cspoils%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20enervating%20Dalit%20movement%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChirag%20Paswan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20style%20of%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%20was%20completely%20different%20from%20that%20of%20Kanshi%20Ram%20and%20Mayawati.%20A%20product%20of%20the%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia-led%20socialist%20movement%2C%20Ram%20Vilas%20kept%20the%20battle%20for%20the%20Dalits%E2%80%99%20cause%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20socialist%20movement.%20For%20large%20parts%20of%20his%20career%2C%20he%20remained%20in%20the%20Lok%20Dal%2C%20Janata%20Party%2C%20and%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20though%20he%20had%20formed%20the%20%E2%80%98Dalit%20Sena%E2%80%99%20to%20espouse%20the%20causes%20of%20the%20Dalits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F25110820%2Fljp.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F25110820%2Fljp.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F25110820%2Fljp-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-487970%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELJP%20leader%20Chirag%20Paswan.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2Fichiragpaswan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20Kanshi%20Ram%20had%20created%20a%20%E2%80%98monolith%E2%80%99%20by%20uniting%20various%20Dalit%20castes%2C%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Dalits%20stayed%20divided%20among%20various%20socialist%20and%20communist%20parties.%20The%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20and%20the%20CPI-ML-Liberation%20all%20have%20voter%20bases%20in%20Dalit%20communities.%20Of%20course%2C%20Ram%20Vilas%20emerged%20as%20the%20strongest%20leader%20of%20the%20Paswan%20caste%20%E2%80%93%20the%20largest%20Dalit%20caste%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%205.31%25%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20population.%20The%20Ravidasis%2C%20who%20are%20equivalent%20to%20the%20Jatavs%20in%20UP%2C%20are%20fewer%20in%20number%20compared%20to%20Paswans%2C%20accounting%20for%205.21%25%20population%20of%20the%20state%20population.%20Paswan%20was%20for%20members%20of%20his%20caste%20what%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20is%20for%20the%20Yadavs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20used%20his%20support%20base%20with%20panache%2C%20aligning%20with%20other%20parties%20according%20to%20his%20suitability%20during%20elections%20but%20maintaining%20a%20vice-like%20grip%20over%20the%20community.%20He%20never%20allowed%20the%20BJP%20or%20other%20parties%20to%20make%20inroads%20into%20his%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%20Vilas%20never%20shied%20away%20from%20promoting%20his%20family%20members%20in%20politics.%20He%20promoted%20his%20brothers%2C%20Pashupati%20Paras%2C%20a%20Union%20minister%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20and%20Ramchandra%20Paswan.%20There%20was%20no%20issue%20in%20his%20party%20when%20he%20got%20his%20son%20Chirag%20to%20contest%20the%20Jamui%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%202014%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20his%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20has%20split%20into%20two%20with%20Chirag%20and%20his%20uncle%20Pashupati%20locked%20in%20a%20turf%20war%20for%20the%20Paswans.%20Both%20Chirag%20and%20Pashupati%20are%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20of%20now%2C%20but%20there%20is%20still%20infighting.%20Who%20will%20inherit%20Ram%20Vilas%E2%80%99s%20legacy%3F%20Will%20it%20be%20Pashupati%20or%20Chirag%3F%20Or%20will%20the%20Paswans%20be%20divided%20among%20various%20parties%3F%20The%20results%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20might%20give%20some%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702985393000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F19143324%2FEffect-32.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmayawati-successor-contrasting-challenges-akash-anand-chirag-paswan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Both%20Akash%20Anand%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Chirag%20Paswan%20in%20Bihar%20face%20a%20unique%20set%20of%20challenges%20to%20protect%20the%20core%20Dalit%20communities%20that%20their%20respective%20parties%20have%20cultivated%20over%20the%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmayawati-successor-contrasting-challenges-akash-anand-chirag-paswan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20are%20Yemen's%20Houthis%20and%20why%20are%20they%20attacking%20Red%20Sea%20ships%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702985127000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106125661%2Cimgsize-42042.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fm