51%2FThe-Wire-77.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20a%20week-long%20conflict%20with%20pro-democracy%20forces%2C%20the%20Myanmar%20army%20has%20failed%20to%20seize%20control%20of%20the%20strategic%20town%20of%20Khampat%20in%20that%20country%E2%80%99s%20Sagaing%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhampat%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Kabaw%20valley%2C%20is%20located%20close%20to%20the%20Indian%20state%20of%20Manipur.%20The%20town%20has%20historically%20been%20under%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20Burmese%20kings%20and%20the%20Manipur%20principality.%20During%20the%20division%20of%20territory%20between%20a%20British-ruled%20Manipur%20and%20the%20Burmese%2C%20the%20Kabaw%20valley%20had%20gone%20to%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20the%20anti-Junta%20groups%20had%20taken%20control%20of%20Khampat.%20In%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20government%20in%20exile%2C%20the%20National%20Unity%20Government%20(NUG)%2C%20the%20NUG-led%20people%E2%80%99s%20defence%20forces%20(PDFs)%20and%20the%20Kachin%20Independence%20Army%20jointly%20seized%20control%20of%20the%20town%20after%20a%20four-day%20fight%20with%20the%20Junta%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20PDF%20personnel%20had%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmyanmar-now.org%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fmyanmar-resistance-forces-take-over-town-near-indian-border%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMyanmar%20Now%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20resistance%20forces%20had%20%E2%80%9Ctaken%20control%20of%20the%20entire%20town%20which%20included%20army%20camps%2C%20police%20stations%2C%20and%20Junta%20administrative%20buildings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2018%2C%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irrawaddy.com%2Fnews%2Fburma%2Fmyanmar-junta-troops-retreat-after-failing-to-retake-strategic-india-border-town.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Irrawaddy%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20the%20NUG%20and%20the%20Chin%20National%20Organisation%20to%20say%20that%20the%20Junta%20